  "title": "Big refactoring/simplification pass",
  "body": "Refactor RefinementList/Menu/Hierarchical/etc. to use a single List component\nand move the show more logic there.\n\nAdd themeable and translatable HOCs to reduce boilerplate and prepare for\nfuture work.\n\nRemove PaginationLink, prefer single component rendering.\n\nAdd defaultProps option to createHOC's output in order to further parameterize\ncustom HOCs and move default props configuration to widgets.\n",
